## Usage Example

Here's a basic usage example of the `DashboardSkeleton`:

```tsx
<Canvas>
  <Story name="Default">
    <DashboardSkeleton 
      sidebarVisible={true}
      chartCount={2}
      tableVisible={true}
      metricCount={4}
      className="w-full h-screen"
    />
  </Story>
</Canvas>
``` 